Cedarville appeared as an unincorporated community in the [[1950 U.S. census]]<ref name=CensusNJ1950CDP/> and the [[1960 U.S. census]].<ref name=CensusNJ1960CDP/> The community did not appear in subsequent censuses until being listed as a [[census designated place]] in the [[2000 U.S. census]].<ref name=CensusNJ2000CDP/>

